net.sf.javaml.core

Class SparseInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.javaml.core.AbstractInstance
      • net.sf.javaml.core.SparseInstance
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Double>, java.util.Map<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Double>, Instance

    public class SparseInstance
extends AbstractInstance
implements Instance
    Implementation of a sparse instance. This implementation maps attribute indices to values. Attributes for which the value is not set return a default value.
    Author:
    Thomas Abeel (thomas@abeel.be)
    See Also:
    Dataset, Instance, Serialized Form
